Package: BCVICalculator
Title: BCVI Stroke Risk Prediction Calculator
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Josh", "Preston", email = "jdpreston30@users.noreply.github.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Wagner", "et al.", role = "aut")
    )
Description: Interactive Shiny application for calculating stroke risk in patients with blunt cerebrovascular injury (BCVI). Implements the prediction model from Wagner et al. 2025.
Depends: 
    R (>= 4.5.1)
